OL,3,CMan charged with attempted rape after
OL,4,Csexual assault near M1 services
OL,6,FA 59-year-old Polish resident has been
OL,7,Fcharged with attempted rape and
OL,8,Fintentional strangulation after a
OL,9,Fwoman was sexually assaulted near the
OL,10,FLeicester Forest East service station
OL,11,Fon the M1.
OL,13,FA woman in her 20s, was grabbed from
OL,14,Fbehind by a man while she walked along
OL,15,FBaines Lane towards Hinckley Road in
OL,16,FLeicestershire.
OL,18,FThe incident happened on an access
OL,19,Froad for the M1 southbound services.
