OL,3,CMan charged with attempted rape after
OL,4,Csexual assault near M1 services
OL,6,FTadeusz Podlasinski, of Wojska
OL,7,FPolskiego, Poland, was arrested by
OL,8,Fpolice on Tuesday (28 April) and has
OL,9,Fremained in police custody.
OL,11,FPodlasinski is due to appear at
OL,12,FLeicester Magistrates' Court today (30
OL,13,FApril).
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
